VShe gave good renditions of &#8216;Sri Chakra Raja Nilaye&#8217; (Sivasakthi) and &#8216;Nee Dhaya Radha&#8217; (Vasantha Bhairavi) and a Ragam-Thanam-Pallavi in Lathangi.The pallavi set to Kanda Thriputa thalam had &#8216;Kadhir Vadi Vela Unadhu Paadham Thunaye&#8217; for its lyrics and included the ragas Bhoopalam, Sahana and Ranjani in the multi raga segement. Usha Rajagoplan on the violin accompanied in a tactful manner and A.S.Ranganathan on the mridangam and Adambakkam Shankar on the ghatam provided neat laya support.
